<div id="review_2857731601" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2857731601" />
    <a title="Dylan Todd" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/98517328-dylan-todd"><img alt="Dylan Todd" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1560490694p2/98517328.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2857731601?book_show_action=true">Jun 14, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dylan Todd" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dylan Todd" href="/user/show/98517328-dylan-todd">Dylan Todd</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2857731601" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2384996073682738729">First Saul book I ever read, about ten or so years ago. It kept me up all night. Anything horror involving children has always been terrifying to me and Saul does it best. Since then I’ve read several more from him.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

